{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1778905026114,"sessionID":"ses_1d10260feffeTFmAt6ufe0Ie5q","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"bash","callID":"functions.bash:14","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"command":"git add src/ontology/uberon-edit.obo && git commit -m \"Remove 'located in' thoracic cavity axiom from esophagus and change esophageal artery relationship to 'connecting branch of' thoracic aorta\n\nAddresses #3572\n\n- UBERON:0001043 (esophagus): Removed 'located in' some 'thoracic cavity' because\nthe esophagus has cervical and abdominal parts in addition to its thoracic part.\n\n- UBERON:0035539 (esophageal artery): Changed 'branching part of' some 'thoracic aorta'\nto 'connecting branch of' some 'thoracic aorta' for consistency with how arteries\nconnecting to and supplying other organs are modeled in UBERON.\"\n","description":"Commit ontology changes"},"output":"[scribe-v1-ai4curation-uberon-agent-config-v3-.-togetherai-moonshotai-Kimi-K2.6-iter1-issue-3572 e8e24ec] Remove 'located in' thoracic cavity axiom from esophagus and change esophageal artery relationship to 'connecting branch of' thoracic aorta\n 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+), 2 deletions(-)\n","metadata":{"output":"[scribe-v1-ai4curation-uberon-agent-config-v3-.-togetherai-moonshotai-Kimi-K2.6-iter1-issue-3572 e8e24ec] Remove 'located in' thoracic cavity axiom from esophagus and change esophageal artery relationship to 'connecting branch of' thoracic aorta\n 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+), 2 deletions(-)\n","exit":0,"description":"Commit ontology changes","truncated":false},"title":"Commit ontology changes","time":{"start":1778905026109,"end":1778905026113}},"id":"prt_e2f0075c7001RaDkYQPQ10NVta","sessionID":"ses_1d10260feffeTFmAt6ufe0Ie5q","messageID":"msg_e2f00687900159YadEahw2sWeS"}}
